OL,6,FNelson has been speaking to ITV
OL,7,FGranada correspondent Tim Scott.
OL,9,FA retired shopkeeper has been told he
OL,10,Fis not British by the Home Office
OL,11,Fdespite being in the UK for nearly 50
OL,12,Fyears
OL,14,FNelson Shardey, 74, assumed he was a
OL,15,Fcitizen for many years but when he
OL,16,Fapplied for a passport in 2019 he was
OL,17,Ftold he had no right to be in the UK.
