OL,3,CRetired shopkeeper told he is not
OL,4,CBritish after 46 years in UK
OL,6,F"I tried to be brave in front of my
OL,7,Fchildren," the 74-year-old said.
OL,8,F"Emotionally, it is really
OL,9,Fdisheartening. It's sucking the blood
OL,10,Fout of me.
OL,12,F"I worked from 1978 until 2022, I have
OL,13,Fpaid my tax. I have done what any
OL,14,Freasonable human being should do."
OL,16,FNelson, who is recovering from
OL,17,Fprostate cancer, moved from Ghana in
OL,18,F1977 to study accountancy, but a coup
OL,19,Fthere meant he could never go back.
