OL,3,CRetired shopkeeper told he is not
OL,4,CBritish after 46 years in UK
OL,6,FThe Home Office told Nelson that he
OL,7,Fwould need to apply for the 10-year
OL,8,Froute to settlement, which would cost
OL,9,Faround #7,000.
OL,11,FNelson also faces paying more than
OL,12,F#10,000 to access the NHS, despite
OL,13,Fpaying taxes all his adult life, so he
OL,14,Fcan have regular cancer check-ups.
OL,16,F"I'm living on #117 a week pension,"
OL,17,FNelson explains. "I had cancer. I have
OL,18,Fbeen going every six months for check
OL,19,Fups.
